---
title: Middle Eastern Beef & Crouton Cos Salad with Yoghurt Hummus & Lemon
description: Are you ready to up your salad game? Let’s marinate tender beef strips in our chermoula spice blend, and layer it onto a crisp cos salad with fresh veggies and crunchy croutons. Add a drizzle of tangy yoghurt hummus for the perfect finishing touch!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*
